      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * Maastricht University</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Gouvernement_Bouillonstraat_Bremer_Maastricht.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/98/Gouvernement_Bouillonstraat_Bremer_Maastricht.jpg/330px-Gouvernement_Bouillonstraat_Bremer_Maastricht.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"399\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/98/Gouvernement_Bouillonstraat_Bremer_Maastricht.jpg/500px-Gouvernement_Bouillonstraat_Bremer_Maastricht.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/98/Gouvernement_Bouillonstraat_Bremer_Maastricht.jpg/960px-Gouvernement_Bouillonstraat_Bremer_Maastricht.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Gouvernement_Bouillonstraat_Bremer_Maastricht.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Maastricht University</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Maastricht University</b>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maastricht\">Maastricht</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Netherlands\">The Netherlands</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Important_UM_Dates\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Important UM Dates</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#People\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">People</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Chess_Programs_and_Authors\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Programs and Authors</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Tournaments\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tournaments</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Conferences\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Conferences</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Important_UM_Dates\">Important UM Dates</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maastricht_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Important UM Dates\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> Until 1996 the University of Limburg in Maastricht <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> In 1996 name change to 'Universiteit Maastricht' <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> 11 January 2008: Name change to 'Maastricht University'</li>\n<li> Until 2008 associated with the Editorial Board of the <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"People\">People</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maastricht_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: People\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection