\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Alex_de_Voogt\" title=\"Alex de Voogt\">Alex de Voogt</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Erik_van_der_Werf\" title=\"Erik van der Werf\">Erik van der Werf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mark_Winands\" title=\"Mark Winands\">Mark Winands</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Programs_and_Authors\">Chess Programs and Authors</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maastricht_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Programs and Authors\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/AliBaba\" title=\"AliBaba\">AliBaba</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Duck\" title=\"Duck\">Duck</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Dennis_Breuker\" title=\"Dennis Breuker\">Dennis Breuker</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Much\" title=\"Much\">Much</a> (<b>M</b>aastricht <b>U</b>niversity <b>Ch</b>ess Program)\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Roger_H%C3%BCnen\" title=\"Roger Hünen\">Roger Hünen</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Harry_Nefkens\" title=\"Harry Nefkens\">Harry Nefkens</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tom_Pronk\" title=\"Tom Pronk\">Tom Pronk</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Touch\" title=\"Touch\">Touch</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tournaments\">Tournaments</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maastricht_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Tournaments\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/3rd_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"3rd Computer Olympiad\">3rd Computer Olympiad</a>, 1992</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/6th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"6th Computer Olympiad\">6th Computer Olympiad</a>, 2001</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/WMCCC_2001\" title=\"WMCCC 2001\">WMCCC 2001</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/7th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"7th Computer Olympiad\">7th Computer Olympiad</a>, 2002</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/WCCC_2002\" title=\"WCCC 2002\">WCCC 2002</a></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Conferences\">Conferences</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maastricht_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Conferences\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/3rd_Computer_Olympiad#Workshop\" title=\"3rd Computer Olympiad\">Heuristic Programming in AI 3</a>, 1992</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_7\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 7\">Advances in Computer Chess 7</a>, 1993</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_8\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 8\">Advances in Computer Chess 8</a>, 1996</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/6th_Computer_Olympiad#Workshop\" title=\"6th Computer Olympiad\">6th Computer Olympiad Workshop</a>, 2001</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/7th_Computer_Olympiad#Workshop\" title=\"7th Computer Olympiad\">7th Computer Olympiad Workshop</a>, 2002</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maastricht_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maastricht_University\">Maastricht University from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.maastrichtuniversity.nl/\">Maastricht University official Page</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://project.dke.maastrichtuniversity.nl/games/\">Games and AI Group</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://project.dke.maastrichtuniversity.nl/games/listPhD.htm\">Games and AI Group - Ph.D. Theses</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://project.dke.maastrichtuniversity.nl/games/games_go.htm\">Go for Go Project</a></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maastricht_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Building Gouvernement, former residence of the Gouvernor of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Limburg_%28Netherlands%29\">Limburg</a>. Now a part of the University. Build around 1935 and designed by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://en.nai.nl/museum/exhibitions/online/item/_rp_kolom2-1_elementId/1_169764\">G.C. Bremer</a>, Image by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Brbbl\">Brbbl</a>, June 14, 2009, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/deed.en\">CC BY-SA 3.0</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons\">Wikimedia Commons</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maastricht_University\">Maastricht University from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.unimaas.nl/default.asp?template=werkveld.htm&amp;id=03IM3245DVHAD1WX4P30&amp;taal=en\">UM History</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.unimaas.nl/default.asp?template=werkveld.htm&amp;id=V3V152R0XROSXONX5360&amp;taal=en\">Important UM dates</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#31_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 31, No. 2</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ticc.uvt.nl/icga/journal/contents/content31-2.htm\">From Maastricht to Tilburg</a> </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/JAIST\" title=\"JAIST\">Japan Advanced Institute of Science and Technology</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://aurora.mlhci.sztaki.hu/www/index.pl/kocsis\">Levente Kocsis from the Hungarian Academy of Science</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228101318\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.068 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.650 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 115/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 242/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00% 